                    <li><a href="https://priv.gc.ca/fr/recherche/">Page de recherche</a></li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-6">
                <h1><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-warning-sign mrgn-rght-md"></span>Internal server error</h1>
                <p>
                    The Web server is incapable of performing the request. Please try your request again later. Please
                    contact the Web server's administrator with the following information if this problem persists:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Event ID: 110000003</li>
                    <li>Event Type: signature</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Here are some links that can help you:</p>
